OL,3,CJersey hospital loses #250,000 to
OL,4,Cwasted chemotherapy medication
OL,6,FJersey's hospital has revealed more
OL,7,Fthan #250,000 has been lost in the
OL,8,Fpast four years through chemotherapy
OL,9,Fmedication waste, according to
OL,10,Fstatistics from a Freedom of
OL,11,FInformation (FOI) request.
OL,13,FThe FOI request was made in relation
OL,14,Fto the Health Department's new system,
OL,15,FBookWise.
OL,17,FIt was reported the system saved the
OL,18,Fhospital #40,000 in chemotherapy
OL,19,Fwastage this year.
