OL,4,Cwasted chemotherapy medication
OL,6,FBookwise replaced the hospital's
OL,7,Fmanual booking systems and paper
OL,8,Fdiaries in October 2023, so changes to
OL,9,Fa patient's treatment status can be
OL,10,Fupdated in real time.
OL,12,FThis means that if a patient's
OL,13,Ftreatment is cancelled, chemotherapy
OL,14,Fdrugs could be saved and returned to
OL,15,Fthe stock.
OL,17,FThe FOI asked for further clarity on
OL,18,Fhow the system works and how much the
OL,19,Fhospital on wasted chemotherapy drugs
OL,20,Fin the past.
