OL,3,CJersey hospital loses #250,000 to
OL,4,Cwasted chemotherapy medication
OL,6,FThe FOI response revealed that the
OL,7,Fhospital saw #250,519 wasted on
OL,8,Fchemotherapy drugs between 2021 and
OL,9,FOctober 2024:
OL,11,FThe FOI states that in the old system,
OL,12,Fproblems could occur if the Pharmacy
OL,13,Fwas not alerted to the cancellation of
OL,14,Ftreatment on the day.
OL,16,FMedication may expire if it is left in
OL,17,Fthe Oncology Unit fridge overnight,
OL,18,Fmeaning it cannot be placed back into
OL,19,Fstock.
